und-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline: 0px;\">Oppo</a>&nbsp;narrative. But the company needs to be a bit cautious about how this will be perceived by potential buyers.</p><span class=\"custom-caption\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px 0px 5px; border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(219, 219, 219); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(116, 116, 116); display: block; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 19px; overflow: hidden;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-7918141 size-full\" src=\"https://images.indianexpress.com/2022/05/OnePlus-10R-Review-camera-array.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-lazy-loaded=\"true\" srcset=\"https://images.indianexpress.com/2022/05/OnePlus-10R-Review-camera-array.jpg 759w, https://images.indianexpress.com/2022/05/OnePlus-10R-Review-camera-array.jpg?resize=450,262 450w, https://images.indianexpress.com/2022/05/OnePlus-10R-Review-camera-array.jpg?resize=600,349 600w, https://images.indianexpress.com/2022/05/OnePlus-10R-Review-camera-array.jpg?resize=695,405 695w, https://images.indianexpress.com/2022/05/OnePlus-10R-Review-camera-array.jpg?resize=150,87 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 759px) 100vw, 759px\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 5px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 100%; height: auto; width: 640px;\">&nbsp;The camera array of the OnePlus 10R. (Image credit: Nandagopal Rajan / Express Photo)</span><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 28px;\">The rear panel of the phone has a distinct design with lines flowing down from below the camera module. On the other side is a matte finish with the brand logo shining through. I liked how lightweight the phone is to hold and it offers a very solid grip thanks to the same sharp edges.</p><div class=\"mceTemp\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"></div><span class=\"custom-caption\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px 0px 5px; border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(219, 219, 219); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(116, 116, 116); display: block; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 19px; overflow: hidden;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-7918144 size-full\" src=\"https://images.indianexpress.com/2022/05/OnePlus-10R-review-display-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-lazy-loaded=\"true\" srcset=\"https://images.indianexpress.com/2022/05/OnePlus-10R-review-display-2.jpg 759w, https://images.indianexpress.com/2022/05/OnePlus-10R-review-display-2.jpg?resize=450,262 450w, https://images.indianexpress.com/2022/05/OnePlus-10R-review-display-2.jpg?resize=600,349 600w, https://images.indianexpress.com/2022/05/OnePlus-10R-review-display-2.jpg?resize=695,405 695w, https://images.indianexpress.com/2022/05/OnePlus-10R-review-display-2.jpg?resize=150,87 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 759px) 100vw, 759px\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 5px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 100%; height: auto; width: 640px;\">&nbsp;The phone offers a solid grip, though it lacks the smooth edges that one is used&nbsp; (Image credit: Nandagopal Rajan / Express Photo)</span><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 28px;\">The 6,7-inch Fluid AMOLED display is as good as you would expect from OnePlus. The 120Hz refresh rate means gamers have another reason to love this phone. The audio output is good and does not underwhelm given the quality of the screen.</p><span class=\"custom-caption\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px 0px 5px; border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(219, 219, 219); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(116, 116, 116); display: block; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 19px; overflow: hidden;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-7918140 size-full\" src=\"https://images.indianexpress.com/2022/05/OnePlus-10R-review-display.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-lazy-loaded=\"true\" srcset=\"https://images.indianexpress.com/2022/05/OnePlus-10R-review-display.jpg 759w, https://images.indianexpress.com/2022/05/OnePlus-10R-review-display.jpg?resize=450,262 450w, https://images.indianexpress.com/2022/05/OnePlus-10R-review-display.jpg?resize=600,349 600w, https://images.indianexpress.com/2022/05/OnePlus-10R-review-display.jpg?resize=695,405 695w, https://images.indianexpress.com/2022/05/OnePlus-10R-review-display.jpg?resize=150,87 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 759px) 100vw, 759px\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 5px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 100%; height: auto; width: 640px;\">&nbsp;As always, OnePlus offers a stunning display for the price. (Image credit: Nandagopal Rajan / Express Photo)</span><h2 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 24px; font-weight: 700;\">OnePlus 10R review: What’s good?</h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 28px;\">Let me start with the USP of this phone — this phone has the 150W SUPERVOOC Endurance Edition charge for its 4500 mAh battery. Yes, you read that right: 150W. Now, this charger is in many ways larger, and certainly, heavier than the phone itself. While the convenience of a phone that can juice up to take on a day in about 15 minutes is hard to ignore, I’m not sure everyone would want a block this size in their bag.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 28px;\">So when I was travelling to Jaipur recently, I kept this charger at home and packed an earlier 65W OnePlus charger for the trip. But what the 150W charger can do is amazing and I watched in awe as the battery level went up by a percentage almost every other second. The phone ends up getting a full charge in 17 minutes flat. Magic.</p><div class=\"custom_read_button\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 10px 0px; border-width: 1px 0px; border-top-style: solid; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: rgb(219, 219, 219); border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(219, 219, 219); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 22px; font-weight: 700;\"><span class=\"widget_title\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(163, 32, 32);\">Also Read&nbsp;</span>|<span class=\"article_title\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><a class=\"click-event-dataid\" data-id=\"Alsoread_editdriven\" href=\"https://indianexpress.com/article/technology/tech-reviews/apple-ipad-air-5th-gen-review-7876122/\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); cursor: pointer; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline: 0px;\">Apple iPad Air 5th Gen review: Best keeps on getting better</a></span></div><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 28px;\">Since this is a phone that goes out of its grain a bit, OnePlus has also partnered with MediaTek to power it with the new Dimensity 8100-Max. Having used the phone for close to two weeks, I can say there is nothing to prevent MediaTek from finding itself powering more flagships in the future. The phone is capable of handling all tasks and multi-tasks like a dream switching between apps as you want it to. The phone is also super cool, especially since I was using it to play games like Extreme Balancer 3 during a hot summer bus journey where the temperatures outside were pushing 45 degrees Celsius.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 28px;\">Then there is the 50MP camera which makes its presence felt every time you see the back of the phone. The 8MP ultra-wide and 2MP macro lenses almost dissolve into the background under the size of the 50MP camera. With so much space being used, I am a bit surprised this is not an ultra-wide lens, because OnePlus could have offered a special experience here.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 28px;\">However, the 50MP camera does a good job of offering sharp images under all conditions. I was walking around clicking pics at the Bishangarh fort one hot summer afternoon and some of the images were stunning.</p></div></div>                                <!-- Place <em>some</em> <u>text</u> <strong>here</strong> -->\r\n                            ', 103, NULL, '', 1, 0, '', '', NULL, '2022-05-16 06:41:06'),
('p5', 124, 'I started tech budgeting and you should do it too', '                               <div class=\"editor\" id=\"storycenterbyline\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 20px; color: rgb(72, 72, 72); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif;\">Written by&nbsp;<a href=\"https://indianexpress.com/profile/author/anuj-bhatia/\" class=\"bulletProj\" id=\"written_by1\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration-line: underline; cursor: pointer; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline: 0px; line-height: 20px; font-weight: 700;\">Anuj Bhatia</a>&nbsp;| New Delhi |<br><span itemprop=\"dateModified\" content=\"2022-05-16T09:44:27+05:30\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 16px;\">Updated: May 16, 2022 9:44:27 am</span></div><p><span itemprop=\"image\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/ImageObject\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif;\"></span><span class=\"custom-caption\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px 0px 5px; border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(219, 219, 219); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(116, 116, 116); display: block; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 19px; overflow: hidden;\"><img src=\"https://images.indianexpress.com/2022/05/WhatsApp-Image-2022-05-15-at-12.10.39-PM.jpeg\" alt=\"tech, tech budgeting, tech budget, streaming services, how to choose the right streaming service, netflix, disney hotstar, personal finance\" width=\"640\" height=\"356\" data-lazy-loaded=\"true\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 5px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 100%; height: auto; width: 640px;\"><span class=\"ie-custom-caption\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Sit down on the weekend and figure out which services to keep and which ones to cancel.</span></span></p><div id=\"pcl-full-content\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif;\"><p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 28px;\">Before going to bed one-night last month, I got a text message: “You have spent Rs 459 via debit card at Amazon.” I read the message and slept. Later, in the morning, when I woke up I read the message again and wondered why Rs 459 was charged to my debit card. I then checked the Amazon app and realised I forgot to turn off auto-renewal. Rs 459 is not a huge sum but it pinched me a lot when the money was deducted from my account for a service I no longer use. That day I realised I need to seriously understand my monthly expenses better, especially the amount spent on services and apps. I am not trying to be a personal finance expert but I want to share my experience and a few tips you can apply to better manage your tech budget.</p><ev-engagement group-name=\"contentLogin\"></ev-engagement><ev-engagement group-name=\"myNotification\"></ev-engagement><div class=\"ev-meter-content\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><h2 class=\"p1\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 24px; font-weight: 700;\"><b style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Understand where your money is going&nbsp;</b></h2><p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 28px;\">Whether you are a student or a working professional, start paying attention to the basic fundamental components of financial literacy. Nobody will tell you what is more important: a coffee at a cafe or paying the EMI of your smartphone before the due date? The point is to understand the benefits of financial literacy so that you know where your money is going. Every penny matters. Until a few months back, I was randomly purchasing vintage gadgets on&nbsp;<a href=\"https://indianexpress.com/about/olx/\" class=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(52, 111, 153); cursor: pointer; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline: 0px;\">OLX</a>&nbsp;and because of that, I messed up my finances. I still buy vintage gadgets but now I look at my bank balance and review my spending before buying anything new.</p><span class=\"custom-caption\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px 0px 5px; border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(219, 219, 219); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(116, 116, 116); display: block; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 19px; overflow: hidden;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-7918075 size-full\" src=\"https://images.indianexpress.com/2022/05/999.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-lazy-loaded=\"true\" srcset=\"https://images.indianexpress.com/2022/05/999.jpg 759w, https://images.indianexpress.com/2022/05/999.jpg?resize=450,250 450w, https://images.indianexpress.com/2022/05/999.jpg?resize=600,334 600w, https://images.indianexpress.com/2022/05/999.jpg?resize=728,405 728w, https://images.indianexpress.com/2022/05/999.jpg?resize=150,83 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 759px) 100vw, 759px\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 5px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 100%; height: auto; width: 640px;\">&nbsp;Disney Hotstar Plus offers three tiers and each plan costs more than the other. (Image credit: Disney)</span><h2 class=\"p1\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 24px; font-weight: 700;\"><b style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Allocating monthly budget for streaming services&nbsp;</b></h2><p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 28px;\">About a month back, I logged into my savings account and started calculating the money I spent on subscriptions. To put it simply, it was a shock, especially the fact that there were so many monthly subscriptions I had forgotten about. It is easy to subscribe to subscription services, but hard to keep using them or to keep a tab of what you are spending on these.</p></div></div>                             ', 103, NULL, '', 1, 0, '', '', NULL, '2022-05-16 06:42:32');
